    <keyword>TOPT-TIM</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This Telnet Option provides a way to check the roundtrip path between two Telnet modules.  This RFC specifies a standard for the ARPA Internet community.  Hosts on the ARPA Internet are expected to adopt and implement this standard.  Obsoletes NIC 16238.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
